summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 35109, entitled: "An ordinance providing for the extending and establishing of West Smith Street and West Smith Street produced, through the west one half of the Southwest quarter of the Northeast quarter of Section Twenty-four (24), Township Twenty-five (25) North, Range Three (3) East, W.M.," approved the 19th day of August, 1915, and published the 23rd day of August 1915.
